column5: What a beast,you sure have the Pike dialed in Steve!!!!!!!!
Great Pike Steve ! but ... pull up your pants !
Nice Pike! Boo on the verticle hold!
Now thats cool. Great pics vid and story.
Awesome pike!!!!!!!!!! Good choice of meal for him too, those Omega 3's doin him some good lol
Nice pike.  So he had that laker in his belly, and still went for your bait
That's something else... very impressive fish
that is one monster fish there sir... perhaps a bigger net next time you're out huntin gators ? jus'ayin
:rofl2:  I'm thinking that might be the mojo Randy.  Good thing he doesn't go commando!!!
Beauty thick beast.  Proof you don't need to spend $$$$ to find big pike.  Good on ya!  I'm more curious how you keep your pants from falling down!  RJ
Wow, that is a real decent fish.
That would also be a pb laker for a few of us.
thats a serious northern. congrats on the pb! imperium seems to be doing very well for you, i gotta try plastic more often for pike.
